name: Paper Plane (itch) (FiPlay)
description:
Paper Plane is a game that is made almost similar to the Flappy Bird game. This game also has the same obstacle, but in this game the obstacle is made more challenging by the movement of the obstacle up and down. The goal of this game is also the same, namely we will get the highest score according to our abilities. 

This game is designed for android platform and made on Unity Game Engine
